     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap mappingInformateurCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"en-mappingInformateurCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcmappingInformateurCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-informateur</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-informant</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMInformateur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>informant</td><td/></tr><tr><td>FRLMInformateur.informateur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>informant.assignedEntity</td><td>L'élément informateur est de type PersonneStructure.</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMInformateur.informateur</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>informant.relatedEntity</td><td>L'élément informateur est de type PersonneStructure.</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-informant</code> to <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/fhir-clinical-document/STU1.1/StructureDefinition-informant-extension.html\">Informant Extensionversion: 1.1.0)</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>informant</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:InformantExtension</td><td/></tr><tr><td>informant.assignedEntity</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:InformantExtension.extension:party.ValueReference</td><td>extension:party.ValueReference.resolve().ofType(PractitionerRole or Patient)</td></tr><tr><td>informant.relatedEntity</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>extension:InformantExtension.extension:party.ValueReference</td><td>extension:party.ValueReference.resolve().ofType(RelatedPerson)</td></tr></table></div>"
